<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/utormentcia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tormentcia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 308<br> <font color=#E9D756>(9/26/01 3:11:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Disappointed</span><hr size=1> Just to chime in my 2 coppers worth, I have to say I'm a bit surprised by Golems being accused of this too.  From my dealings with him, he's always been decent and in fact, has helped a few raids out when they were in trouble.  <br>
<br>
